          <li>Write the distribution.</li>
          <li>Graph the distribution.</li>
          <li>Find <em>P</em> (<m>x</m> &gt; 19).</li>
          <li>Find the 50th percentile.</li>
        </ol>
      </statement>
      <solution>
        <ol>
          <li>Let <m>X</m> = the time needed to change the oil in a car.</li>
          <li>
            <em>X</em> ~ <m>U</m> (11, 21).</li>
          <li />
          <li>
            <em>P</em> (<m>x</m> &gt; 19) = 0.2</li>
          <li>the 50th percentile is 16 minutes.</li>
        </ol>
      </solution>
    </exercise>
  
