            <li>Suppose it is known that the individual lost more than 10 pounds in a month. Find the probability that he lost less than 12 pounds in the month.</li>
            <li>
              <m>P</m>(7 &lt; <m>x</m> &lt; 13|<m>x</m> &gt; 9) = __________. State this result in a probability question, similarly to Parts g and h, draw the picture, and find the probability.</li>
